"  Chips:","1/2 teaspoon dried crushed rosemary","1/4 teaspoon salt","1/4 teaspoon garlic powder","1/8 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","3  (6-inch) pitas, each cut into 8 wedges","  Cooking spray","  Dip:","2  applewood-smoked bacon slices, chopped (such as Nueske's)","4  garlic cloves, minced","1/3 cup fat-free, less-sodium chicken broth","1  (19-ounce) can cannellini beans, drained","1/4 cup chopped green onions","1 tablespoon fresh lemon juice","1/2 teaspoon hot sauce","1/8 teaspoon salt","1/8 teaspoon paprika"